To wire it in:

- Save as `manifest.webmanifest` at your site root (e.g., `/static/manifest.webmanifest` or `/manifest.webmanifest`).[3][1]
- Reference in HTML:

```html
<link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.webmanifest">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#040509">
```

This manifest is production‑ready and aligned with current PWA guidelines for installability and usability.[1][2][4]

